&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review, code, and process vendor invoices in accordance with organizational policies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solicit and process vendor W-9s and ACH forms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconcile vendor statements and resolve invoice discrepancies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond to vendor inquiries in a timely and professional manner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure adherence to internal controls and accounting policies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with audit requests and year-end reporting requirements (1099 and NEC forms)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
